{
  "stem": "12289.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which I-- I'm-- I suppose you are going to ask me about, later on, about the Raoul Wallenberg mission and all that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had always the-- the contact with the embassies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All embassies were in contact with each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had-- we had, constantly, routine-- routine connections, meetings with the other diplomats and so on at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one person some-- which-- whom I-- we became good friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got help from many of them, of these regular diplomats, who were not Nazis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, they were belonging to the party.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were forced to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I especially remember one person, who was attache at the German Embassy in Stockholm, when I was young, studying at university.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I met him here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His name was Bruenhoff.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he then was transferred to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the second time I met him was when I came-- my-- I came to Berlin and met him there for the second time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we developed a-- a little bit of a friendship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- then he--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The third time I met him was in Budapest, when he came being head-- the head of the press section for the German Embassy in-- in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- he helped me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Especially, he helped me one-- at-- at one crucial moment, when we-- we saved the-- the Hungarian Nobel Prize winner, Albert Szent-Gyorgy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We saved him when we-- we got the instructions from Sweden to save him, because he-- he had his prize.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was awarded the Swedish-- he got Swedish citizenship like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had the legal rights to-- to try to-- to protect him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were hiding him at the embassy.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
